 som lyser med sine 10 poeng.", "I natt dr\u00f8mte jeg om et rutebrett med en haug med helvetes dobbeltve-er under, og ingen ord \u00e5 bruke dem p\u00e5. At spillet godtar wca, men ikke wtf er nesten ikke til \u00e5 holde ut.", "terje.eidsvaag@adresseavisen.no"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "41d323ecc8eded070b9cc80ba9ace8ffbdc9968819cb7fc68a21ba9af23827d6"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-12-04T17:00:00.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Som en slags sudoku for humanister er Wordfeud en fascinerende tidstyv. En av ulempene er at du begynner \u00e5 dr\u00f8mme om bokstaver."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article2127919.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/sistestikk0601_seksjon"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/7c3613dca9a58755f09227149dda361d4e11db45.jpg?59772fd8"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Helvetes dobbeltve -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "7c3613dca9a58755f09227149dda361d4e11db45"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["meninger", "snakk ut", "leder"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "meninger,snakk ut,leder"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "hobbies-and-interests"}, {"field": "kw-company", "value": "facebook"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["ord", "wordfeud", "spille", "helvetes dobbeltve"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["wordfeud", "twitter", "angry birds", "scrabble", "cheat for wordfeud"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["norway", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "h\u00e5kon bertheussen"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article2127919.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-de